    "body": "The `screen` module needs to subscribe to native screen events when it is initialized, which requires the app to be ready.\n\nOf course we can return a proxy object and then routing the actual events to it when app is ready, but it adds lots of complexity to the simple module and I don't think it deserves the method.\n"
